Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.48,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,Serial Killer!! {\c&H838C8D&}in Akihabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:06.52,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That serial killer showed up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:09.24,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We don't die, so it's kind of hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.57,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But that makes it even scarier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.42,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,How many victims have there been?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:17.49,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they wouldn't do it at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:21.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's hurting our sales, and ruining our Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:25.27,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But why doesn't the Royal Guard show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:26.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:32.84,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Guard is a security system \Nfrom when this world was a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.56,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They immediately detect any violent acts \Ncommitted within no-combat zones,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:39.68,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and teleport in to neutralize the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:45.73,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They have equipment called "movable armor" \Nthat allows them to use external magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:49.33,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to greatly increase their physical abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:53.93,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,This gives the Royal Guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.99,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who are People of the Land, \Npower that exceeds that of adventurers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.45,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing them to keep the city safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:34.98,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's Christmas Eve, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.71,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And look what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.17,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No sign of anything so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Moving to the next block.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.46,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,When you go looking for them, \Nthey don't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't even a quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:48.52,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And it's kind of cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.07,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Status! Identify him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.24,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He's—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:04.74,Title,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1573,1)}Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:09.12,SignB,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\c&H47895D&}Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:14.63,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They were some of \Nmy guild's best adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That puts the death count over ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Embert Nelreth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No guild affiliation, samurai class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.53,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,level 94.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.28,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the information we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:31.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, the bigger problem is that we know \Nthis much and still can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:32.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:36.47,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And even if he killed us, that wouldn't be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Not for us adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Part of me thinks we aren't worried enough, \Nbut that's better than panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:47.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But if we can't solve this soon, \NI don't think that will last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuation is one possibility, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.26,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon Akihabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Only as an emergency measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:57.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We could move to Shibuya temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.20,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're being too dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, that's not something those of us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in this room can decide on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:10.70,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Still, maybe we should at least \Nevacuate the lower-leveled kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.81,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's worth discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:16.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But still, serial killings in Akihabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.51,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We need to think of some way to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:25.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's the villain in glasses doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:28.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He keeps missing the conferences \Nthat he initiated himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:31.45,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's, um... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,He's out and about, trying to deal \Nwith our financial problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:39.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's December, and the \NChristmas event is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Zantleaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:44.70,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:51.07,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone below level 50 is being asked \Nto help take out the goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:54.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just an excuse to get \Nus away from the serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:58.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's at the heart of it, I'd imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want special treatment, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We can also—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.55,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.15,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to defeat the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.05,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.66,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Because you'll come back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:19.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.17,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:27.03,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how a front-line fighter should think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:33.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If I rush in and die, the party \Nwon't be able to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.81,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.05,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just the fact that you revive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means that, essentially, you're \Ngetting special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:46.93,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,By getting used to that, \Nthinking of it as normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to me that you lose \Nsomething in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:06:00.01,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki didn't come home again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.63,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas Eve. Want to get \Nsomething to eat somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.30,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.30,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I-I'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:10.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Training on Christmas? You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.80,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:13.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Screw that murderer. \NWhere the hell is the Royal Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.70,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.72,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,All these unneeded presences...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:23.21,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Would my lord be angry that I keep doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.74,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to protect Princess Lenessia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.36,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,What did he want me to protect her from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.74,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that People of the Land are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:39.20,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But I think she has plenty of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.99,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have the right to protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.05,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Or the right to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.30,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.81,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is very skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:02.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your guard up at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Assume that his abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.19,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,exceed your own, and even mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you stay with your group, \Nand report in constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:15.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Nazuna will coordinate communications at HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to be heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.22,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you end up in combat with the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.67,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,use formation alpha to delay him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.97,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,For this operation, we've put \Ntwo healers in every team,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.46,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,so you won't have enough attack power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.59,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Your job is to delay him and contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.72,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.99,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.50,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. All right, Souji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:43.23,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I think you said everything I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Just one thing, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The target attacked one of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Murder him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.77,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You can send me out already, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I want revenge on that murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.68,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You just died and came back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.17,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.55,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But Sou's out there fighting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.78,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:39.28,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which of us had been attacked, \Nhe'd never forgive the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.22,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nice to every girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:52.55,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But let me dream, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:57.80,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're amazing, putting \NChristmas and pork soup together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.31,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I put in salmon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.54,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Souji's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:07.19,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But not because he's simply a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:11.32,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the kind of boy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:15.82,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, once he gets mad, \Nthere's no telling what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.78,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fine line between his kindness \Nand that terrifying side of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:25.33,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,If those two were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:29.57,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who could talk him \Nout of it, or affect him at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.03,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,are Kazuhiko and Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.34,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.21,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be back by New Year's,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.93,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I think. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:40.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.44,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't find the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are you continuing patrols?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.48,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.08,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki's working hard, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:00.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You be careful, too, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:02.87,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Souji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.20,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like he's appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.27,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll order the search team to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.92,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We, in the main unit, \Nwill surround and obliterate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:19.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Princess Lenessia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.22,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Kinjou, with the Kunie Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.43,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,What brings him here unannounced, and so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to visit you so suddenly, \Nat this hour of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A serious matter has come up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've come to explain and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.95,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:45.45,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You are familiar with the Defenders, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:50.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the adventurers prefer \Nto call them the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.08,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.46,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I know they're a critical \Npart of the city's security.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:01.05,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A set of movable armor was stolen \Nfrom one of their guardhouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.21,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We believe one of the Royal Guard stole it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:09.02,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,a member of the Kunie Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A Defender's movable armor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must receive a supply of magic at all times \Nfrom a massive magic circle under the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Each city's is slightly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:34.22,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean there's no point \Nin taking it outside the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:38.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But it also means that, inside the \Ntown, its power is unmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:42.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It exceeds that of an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.64,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Then the murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:47.15,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:51.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Kunie Clan is involved in that crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:54.75,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing, but I can say this with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:59.85,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,That means one of the People of \Nthe Land killed an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.38,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This affair is our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.97,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Is there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, is there anything the Kunie Clan can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.92,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Princess Lenessia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.63,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if we shut off the magic supply,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:27.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,the movable armor would cease to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:31.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, it would \Ndisable the city's magic defenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:34.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,allowing monsters to enter the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.62,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't you reboot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.69,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just turn it back on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:44.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,All I can say is that it would take decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.48,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I hadn't heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.13,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.59,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But what can I do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.80,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to protect Princess Lenessia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.35,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.86,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's over for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.86,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.98,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:20.62,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Why, when I came here, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.11,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.43,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you get me out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.87,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you go easy on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.93,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to the Round Table.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:40.85,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But if I do that, won't it mean \Nfighting the adventurers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:43.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:47.20,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell them, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:53.27,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't that monster here when I need him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:57.77,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,When I didn't need him, he was always around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:01.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Crusty went to Seventh Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.17,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.71,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.28,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.97,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.03,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.73,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for entering without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:28.23,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Did you... hear all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:28.88,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.39,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:42.27,SignC,L,0000,0000,0000,,Red Bean Bun
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:49.53,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:52.34,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet things make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.28,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:57.09,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But the rest of the world isn't so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The killer is a Person of the Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.03,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:10.30,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.73,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:16.78,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Who stole it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:21.06,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,They don't know what he wants or where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's hiding in the sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:32.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If we assume he won't leave the city \Nbecause he'd lose his combat powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,that limits the places he can hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:37.17,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The only place that hasn't been searched,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:40.21,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,where people wouldn't see him, is the sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.08,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we can catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.90,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Royal Guard can teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.83,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,So even if we surrounded him, he could escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.73,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:58.17,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,She bears such a heavy burden \Non her tiny shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.70,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But she was doing her best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.87,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with those tiny shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is upsetting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.80,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.75,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've seen you doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.43,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Tanks, switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu, draw aggro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.34,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.71,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Look over here, big guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.65,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Isami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.32,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:04.71,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Something about him isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:08.38,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We hit him a bunch of times, \Nbut his HP hasn't gone down at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.69,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And his status display looks weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.73,SignD,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Embert Nelreth/ Samurai, Lv. 94
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:15.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And we've been fighting so boldly, \Nbut the Royal Guard still isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Without the commander's support, \Nwe would've been in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.86,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.77,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.77,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,In a narrow alley like this, \Nyou'll just get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.90,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to Souji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.91,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.91,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really a samurai, like Sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.74,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Souji's Teaching. A defensive ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:46.04,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Sou said it allows you to see \Nthe trails that form in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.32,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But he isn't getting a chance to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:55.55,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, he'd deflect or dodge, \Ninstead of blocking with his blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:56.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:00.43,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.05,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Sou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.77,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier I put on Souji is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:08.26,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That should have protected \Ntwenty percent of his HP.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.07,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.69,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He needs to think about retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:14.69,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:20.57,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If he does, that guy will just turn \Naround and attack everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.58,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee that \NSouji can stop him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.39,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do for business after Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're changing job classes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's beautiful! This is for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Christmas is that thing the adventurers \Nare all excited about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, anyway? Does it taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.09,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Souji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.73,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,From Shiroe's guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.46,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Axel Fang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.40,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stealth Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.91,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Quick Assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.83,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... She can also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:08.83,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Gust Step!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:17.21,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Without my barrier, that would've killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.22,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.74,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,And that katana...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.47,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.98,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Because defeating him and solving \Nthe problem are different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.66,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Assassinate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:50.41,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, that's the only skill I can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.34,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I said run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.42,Default,So,0000,0000,0000,,I can't agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.47,Default,So,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw, Nazuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:19:59.42,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:02.43,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting at the guild hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.60,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,He was watching his friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.06,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,During a battle like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.17,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,To draw the enemy's attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:10.43,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and wait for the right moment for their retreat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.12,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,He knows he can't win,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.94,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,but for his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.85,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:24.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to give some kind \Nof present to his protégé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:32.02,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Not that there's much I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.56,Default - italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Votive Sword Kogarasumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.19,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Watch carefully, listen carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,wish strongly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and keep thinking about what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:57.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Continue to train, without giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:13.51,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's pathetic how little of an explanation that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.52,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But this is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the entirety of the Teachings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.85,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:44.30,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be real...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:02.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told this is what you people say on this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:17.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing now, my lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:23.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:27.44,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:08.84,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki wanders a town of illusions.
